Episodes.Title: Diego Saves the River Dolphin
Episodes.Plot: Baby River Dolphin got stuck in a puddle after a rainstorm! But he must get back home because today is the day he'll turn pink like a BIG River Dolphin

Episodes.Title: Diego and Baby Humpback to the Rescue
Episodes.Plot: A sunken ship traps King Humpback Whale's tail at the bottom of the ocean.
Episodes.ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification. Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.

Episodes.Title: Little Kinkajou is in Beehive Trouble
Episodes.Plot: Diego must help Little Kinkajou get his head out of a beehive before the bees return.

Episodes.Title: Mackey the Macaroni Penguin
Episodes.Plot: Using Click, Diego finds a lost newborn penguin, Macky the Macaroni Penguin. Diego must take her back home and meet Alicia there to see all the other baby penguins being born.
Episodes.ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification. Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.

Episodes.Title: The Iguana Sing Along
Episodes.Plot: Diego helps Iggy the Iguana find his way out of a cold and dark cave and back to his Iguana friends in time for the big Iguana sing along.

Episodes.Title: Panchita Prairie Dog Finds a New Prairie
Episodes.Plot: Diego and Alicia set out in search of a new home for Panchita the prairie dog in this Old West-themed adventure.

Episodes.Title: Diego Saves Christmas
Episodes.Plot: Linda the Llama and Diego set out to rescue Santa and his reindeer when his sleigh stacked high with toys gets stuck in the deep snow.
Episodes.ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification. Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.

Episodes.Title: Baby Jaguar's Lost Growl
Episodes.Plot: The Bobo brothers are up to no good again when they capture baby jaguar's growl and seal it in a magical bottle. It's up to Diego to get his growl back for him.

Episodes.Title: Diego the Hero
Episodes.Plot: Diego, along with the aid of Baby Jaguar, Mommy Maned Wolf, Sammy the Sloth, Baby Humpback Whale, and Linda the Llama, help rescue Alicia and some injured penguins, who are stuck in the ice on a boat and need to be taken to the Snowy Rescue Center.

Episodes.Title: Sammy's Valentine
Episodes.Plot: Sammy the Sloth has a Valentine's Day gift for Lulu, but he needs Diego's help to deliver it to her.

Episodes.Title: The Great Roadrunner Race
Episodes.Plot: Roady the roadrunner is getting ready for his big race, but first he and Diego need to face many obstacles in the desert in order to make it to the race in time.

Episodes.Title: The Tapir's Trip Home
Episodes.Plot: Diego and the Tapir travel by Chucho the Train to find the perfect environment for the Tapir to call home.

Episodes.Title: Jorge the Little Hawk Learns to Migrate
Episodes.Plot: Diego must build a bird plane so he can follow Jorge the Little Hawk as they set out in search of a warmer climate for him to live in.

Episodes.Title: Giant Octopus to the Rescue
Episodes.Plot: Before the volcanoes erupt, Diego and the Giant Octopus must come to the rescue of animals that have become trapped in coral caves.

Episodes.Title: An Underwater Mystery
Episodes.Plot: Lucy the Fish has no idea what kind of fish she is, so it's up to Diego and Alicia to figure it out from certain clues and then help her find her way back to the proper home.

Episodes.Title: Diego's African Safari (1)
Episodes.Plot: Where are all the African elephants? A mean magician turned them into rocks, so Diego, Alicia, and a Baby Jaguar join Animal Rescuer Juma to find Erin the Elephant and a hidden magic drum that can break the spell and help all the animals in Africa. They'll need your help on this big Safari Rescue!

Episodes.Title: Diego's African Safari (2)
Episodes.Plot: Where are all the African elephants? A mean magician turned them into rocks, so Diego, Alicia, and a Baby Jaguar join Animal Rescuer Juma to find Erin the Elephant and a hidden magic drum that can break the spell and help all the animals in Africa. They'll need your help on this big Safari Rescue!

Episodes.Title: Diego and Alicia Save the Otters
Episodes.Plot: Diego and Alicia must save two baby otters that became separated when the Bobo brothers were messing around in the water and create a huge wave.

Episodes.Title: Alicia Saves the Crocodile
Episodes.Plot: Kyra the Crocodile is lost and Alicia must travel to the dirty city pond to help her find her way back home.
